# 📱 FixMo – AI-Powered Civic Reporting App for Mauritius 🇲🇺

> A beautiful, modern, and civic-impacting mobile app that allows citizens of Mauritius to report street-level problems (potholes, broken lights, garbage, etc.) to the right municipality — powered by AI, maps, and a clean user experience.

---

## 🧰 Full Tech Stack

| Layer       | Technology                  | Description |
|-------------|-----------------------------|-------------|
| **Mobile App** | Flutter (Dart)            | Modern UI framework for Android & iOS from a single codebase |
| **Backend API** | Node.js + Express        | Handles report processing, email sending, and logic |
| **Database** | Supabase (PostgreSQL)       | Stores user accounts, reports, image metadata |
| **Storage** | Supabase Storage             | Stores user-uploaded photos |
| **Authentication** | Supabase Auth         | Email/password or OTP login support |
| **AI** | OpenAI API                        | Used for auto-classifying photos and generating polite complaint messages |
| **Maps SDK** | Google Maps SDK (Flutter)   | Shows map and user’s pin |
| **Geo API** | Google Places / Geocoding API | Converts GPS coordinates to region name to find matching municipality |
| **Email Service** | Nodemailer / Mailgun API | Sends formatted email reports to municipality addresses |
| **Web Admin Dashboard** | Next.js (React)   | Admin portal for municipalities to manage incoming reports |

